{"tid":1078469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人神共憤】日本幼稚園學生集體辱華","createTime":"2019-03-26T10:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T10:26:12.000Z","uid":2054,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"236d9c9e6451b7aa8d34adfc64809cd1f5cedec6","tid":1078469,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/beach_6FlE6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbeach_6FlE6_1200x0.png&h=287bd4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有香港日本人幼稚園學生在老師帶領下，日前到馬鞍山烏溪沙沙灘遊玩，離開時不但不留下半點垃圾，甚至把其他人之前遺下的垃圾都一併帶走，獲網民激讚有公德心。<br />\n<br />\n有網友昨日在Facebook 群組「馬鞍山之友」貼出三張相片，寫道日本幼兒在老師帶領下，到馬鞍山一處海灘遊玩。離開時，孩子們「自己物品自己拎，手拖手，相互照顧」；而且「不單止不留下一點垃圾，連之前有人留下的都一起帶走了。」<br />\n<br />\n帖子刊登才一天，已獲得超過二千個讚好。不少網民激讚日本人學校的教育質素，學生的公德心反映良好教養；亦有人感嘆大陸遊客行為舉止不及一個幼稚園生。憑著相片中幼稚園生的背包，有網民認出該校應是位於紅磡的日本人學校「こひつじ幼稚園」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E7%94%9F%E9%81%8A%E7%83%8F%E6%BA%AA%E6%B2%99-%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%99%82%E5%8B%A4%E5%8A%9B%E6%B8%85%E8%B5%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%8C%87%E6%B2%99%E7%81%98%E4%B9%BE%E6%B7%A8%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E7%25A8%259A%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2581%258A%25E7%2583%258F%25E6%25BA%25AA%25E6%25B2%2599-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%258B%25A4%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%2598%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2589%258D%2F&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhs1lVRHyxjHm7NpFearlrcU%3D&h=8783db37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B9%25